<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shipping Policy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
        }
        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 15px;
                margin: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
        <p>We strive to ensure that your orders are delivered in a timely manner. Please read our shipping policy for more details.</p>
        
        <h2>Shipping Time</h2>
        <p>Orders are processed within 1-2 business days. Standard shipping takes 5-7 business days, while express shipping takes 2-3 business days.</p>
        
        <h2>Shipping Costs</h2>
        <p>Shipping charges are calculated at checkout based on the weight and destination of the package.</p>
        
        <h2>International Shipping</h2>
        <p>We offer international shipping to select countries. Additional customs and duty fees may apply.</p>
        
        <h2>Order Tracking</h2>
        <p>Once your order is shipped, a tracking number will be sent to your email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
